import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import { Play } from 'lucide-react'; import './GameCards.css'; const GameCards = () => { const [isVisible, setIsVisible] = useState(false); const [osuStats, setOsuStats] = useState(null); useEffect(() => { setTimeout(() => setIsVisible(true), 300); // Fetch osu! stats from backend fetch(`${process.env.REACT_APP_BACKEND_URL}/api/osu-stats`) .then(res => res.json()) .then(data => setOsuStats(data)) .catch(err => console.error('Failed to fetch osu! stats:', err)); }, []); const valorantData = { rank: 'Gold 1', date: '28/12/2025', mains: 'Duelists, Initiators.', sensitivity: '0.25 @ 800 DPI', clipUrl: 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tH-ItLBR8gLLnF-rQ_UYKLigqP4xDht8/view?usp=sharing' }; const osuData = { clipUrl: 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jeKlobPM_ok88mVFDvcxv4lVK_8dIc_k/view?usp=sharing', keyboard: 'Attack Shark X65HE', tablet: 'Wacom CTL-4100WL', aimingStyle: 'Drag' }; return (

Game Stats

{/* VALORANT Card */}

VALORANT

Current Rank: {valorantData.rank}
Last Updated: {valorantData.date}
Mains: {valorantData.mains}
Sensitivity: {valorantData.sensitivity}
{/* osu! Card */}

osu!

{osuStats ? ( <>
Global Rank: #{osuStats.pp_rank?.toLocaleString() || 'N/A'}
Country Rank: #{osuStats.pp_country_rank?.toLocaleString() || 'N/A'} ({osuStats.country})
PP: {Math.round(osuStats.pp_raw)}pp
Accuracy: {parseFloat(osuStats.accuracy).toFixed(2)}%
) : (
Loading stats...
)}
Keyboard: {osuData.keyboard}
Tablet: {osuData.tablet}
Aiming Style: {osuData.aimingStyle}
{/* Other Games Card */}

Other Games

Not Coming Soonâ„¢

); }; export default GameCards;
